This project needs the CPAN OpenGL, OpenGL::Image and PNG::Image modules 

If you do not have these modules,
run the following commands in a shell :

perl -MCPAN -e 'install OpenGL';
perl -MCPAN -e 'install OpenGL::Image;'
perl -MCPAN -e 'install Image::PNG';

To run the game :

perl src/Game.pl;

or 

perl src/Gamewithglut.pl;

keyboard bindings:

